SELECT B.ORDER_NUMBER, B.AIR_FLAG, B.REQUEST_SHIPMENT_NUMBER, B.REQUEST_DESTINATION_CD, B.CDNO, B.ORDERED_DATE, B.REMARKS, A.HINBAN, A.QTY, A.REMARKS, B.SECOND_DESTINATION_ADDRESSEE FROM ( SELECT * FROM KOKUSAI.TADD_ORDER_DETAIL WHERE HINBAN Like 'KSP%' AND CANCELED_DATE=0 ) A INNER JOIN KOKUSAI.TADD_ORDER B ON A.ORDER_NUMBER = B.ORDER_NUMBER WHERE B.CDNO Like '%0000-0000'
ORDER BY B.ORDERED_DATE, B.ORDER_NUMBER, B.CDNO, A.HINBAN
